## 5. Technical SEO Checklist

### Fundamentals

- [ ] XML sitemap generated and submitted
- [ ] robots.txt configured correctly
- [ ] Canonical URLs set on all pages
- [ ] Proper heading hierarchy (single H1 per page)
- [ ] Meta titles and descriptions on all pages
- [ ] Open Graph and Twitter Card meta tags
- [ ] Favicon and apple-touch-icon

### Performance

- [ ] Core Web Vitals passing (LCP < 2.5s, INP < 200ms, CLS < 0.1)
- [ ] Images optimized with next/image
- [ ] Fonts self-hosted or preloaded
- [ ] Minimal render-blocking resources

### Crawlability

- [ ] Clean URL structure (no query params for content pages)
- [ ] Proper 301 redirects for moved pages
- [ ] 404 page with helpful navigation
- [ ] No orphan pages (every page reachable from navigation)
- [ ] Pagination handled with rel="next"/"prev" or load more

### Mobile

- [ ] Mobile-friendly design (responsive)
- [ ] Viewport meta tag set
- [ ] Touch targets >= 48px
- [ ] No horizontal scroll

